import React from 'react' import { Table } from 'reactstrap' import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'; import { useSelector } from 'react-redux'; const DataTable = () => { const ticketDetails = useSelector(state => state.busTicket.ticketDetails) return (<> { ticketDetails?.map((details, i) => ) }
# First Name Number Date
{i + 1} {details?.name} {details?.number} {details?.date} {details?.pichupPoint} {details?.dropPoint}
) } export default DataTable
